entries.fs_response20: I've never seen so much blood! Oh, it's horrible!
entries.fs_response19: Are they all gone? How do we know!? They could still be here!
entries.fs_response18: It's useless! How can we fight them? We should just surrender.
entries.fs_response17: Where is Seropf? SEROPF!? Where are you!? I have to find him!

entries.fs_response14: Please... no more! I can't take it anymore!
entries.fs_response13: Where are my children? Has anyone seen my children?
entries.fs_response12: What do they want? We're just farmers.
entries.fs_response11: What did we do to deserve this?

entries.fs_response09: They blew through the defenses like they weren't even there!
entries.fs_response08: They said they were Sith. Sith! We're all going to die!

entries.fs_response06: Where did they come from? Why do they want to hurt us!?
